entries.title: Rohingya mother and daughter rescued after being adrift on boat for almost a month
entries.description: A Rohingya mother and her five-year-old daughter have been found among 200 people rescued in Indonesia after being adrift on a boat for almost a month.

entries.title: Iranian chess players compete without hijab
entries.description: Two Iranian women chess players have competed in an international tournament without a hijab.

entries.title: 'Oh my God! Oh my God!' Footage shows moment huge avalanche buries skiers under snow
entries.description: Dramatic footage shows the moment several skiers were buried under an avalanche in the Austrian Alps on Christmas Day.

entries.title: Zero COVID absolutely hammered China but rapid dropping of containment laws reveals extent of pressure it was under
entries.description: The latest changes to how China is classifying and responding to COVID19 is yet more indication that there will be no going back on the government's sudden and dramatic U-turn.

entries.title: Serbia places security forces on Kosovo border at state of 'full combat readiness'
entries.description: Serbian security forces on the border with Kosovo have been placed on a state of "full combat readiness".

entries.title: Taiwan will extend length of compulsory military service amid growing pressure from China
entries.description: Taiwan is preparing to extend the length of compulsory military service from four months to one year, according to a senior government official.

entries.title: Parts of the US could see another nine inches of snowfall as Biden authorises federal support
entries.description: Parts of the US could see nine inches of new snow today, in a sign that the winter blizzard causing chaos across North America is not over yet.
